                        <p class="mb-0 fw-semibold">BS Information Technology</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">Lyceum of Alabang | 2024 - Present</small>
                        <hr />
                        <p class="mb-0 fw-semibold">Senior High School</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">Lakeview Integrated School | 2020 - 2022</small>
                        <hr />
                        <p class="mb-0 fw-semibold">Junior High School</p>
                        <small class="text-muted">Lakeview Elementary School | 2016 - 2020</small>
